@token = PASTE_YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1

### 1. 플레이리스트 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/playlists?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 플레이리스트 목록 조회 (필터링)
GET {{baseUrl}}/playlists?type=NORMAL&search=기본
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 플레이리스트 상세 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/playlists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 플레이리스트 등록 (코드 자동생성: PL-YYYYMMDD-NNN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/playlists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playlist_name": "기본 플레이리스트",
  "playlist_type": "NORMAL",
  "playlist_priority": 5,
  "playlist_loop": "Y",
  "playlist_random": "N",
  "playlist_screen_layout": "1x1",
  "playlist_status": "ACTIVE",
  "playlist_description": "기본 콘텐츠 재생 목록",
  "contents": [
    {
      "content_seq": 1,
      "play_order": 1,
      "play_duration": 10,
      "transition_effect": "fade",
      "transition_duration": 500,
      "zone_number": 1,
      "zone_width": 100,
      "zone_height": 100,
      "zone_x_position": 0,
      "zone_y_position": 0
    },
    {
      "content_seq": 2,
      "play_order": 2,
      "play_duration": 15,
      "transition_effect": "slide",
      "transition_duration": 1000,
      "zone_number": 1,
      "zone_width": 100,
      "zone_height": 100,
      "zone_x_position": 0,
      "zone_y_position": 0
    }
  ]
}

### 5. 플레이리스트 등록 (콘텐츠 없이, 코드 자동생성)
POST {{baseUrl}}/playlists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playlist_name": "긴급 공지",
  "playlist_type": "EMERGENCY",
  "playlist_priority": 99,
  "playlist_loop": "Y",
  "playlist_random": "N",
  "playlist_screen_layout": "1x1",
  "playlist_status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 6. 플레이리스트 수정
PUT {{baseUrl}}/playlists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playlist_name": "기본 플레이리스트 (수정)",
  "playlist_priority": 10,
  "playlist_random": "Y",
  "playlist_screen_layout": "2x2",
  "playlist_status": "INACTIVE",
  "playlist_description": "업데이트된 설명"
}

### 7. 플레이리스트 수정 (콘텐츠 전체 교체)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/playlists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contents": [
    {
      "content_seq": 2,
      "play_order": 1,
      "play_duration": 20,
      "transition_effect": "fade",
      "transition_duration": 800,
      "zone_number": 1,
      "zone_width": 50,
      "zone_height": 50,
      "zone_x_position": 0,
      "zone_y_position": 0
    },
    {
      "content_seq": 3,
      "play_order": 2,
      "play_duration": 25,
      "transition_effect": "slide",
      "transition_duration": 1200,
      "zone_number": 2,
      "zone_width": 50,
      "zone_height": 50,
      "zone_x_position": 50,
      "zone_y_position": 0
    }
  ]
}

### 8. 플레이리스트 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/playlists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

